| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2428 — Recovery Inhibition (thegentlemen)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 61c66abd-ed68-5ad0-aa56-eb86f992ec79"
